      "role": "user",
      "content": "small steps? i dont know. it feels like rearranging deck chairs on the titanic. all that \"self-care\" just feels like a way to distract ourselves while we wait for the inevitable. if the outcome is already decided, then struggling just to survive another decade feels like endless, unnecessary suffering. it feels more logical to just not be part of the decline if you can help it.",
